caption.title:
Effects of Roundup (A) and equivalent quantities of glyphosate (B) on JEG3 placental cell viability in a serum-containing medium. This was evaluated by the MTT assay, the results are presented as percentages compared with nontreated cells. Cells were incubated with increasing concentrations of Roundup or equivalent concentrations of glyphosate for 18, 24, or 48 hr (n = 9). The LD50 is indicated by a dashed line. Error bars indicate SE.
*p < 0.05;
**p < 0.01.
